      </p>
    </HeaderContent>
  </Header>
  <div class="layout.main offset.after-21">
    <h2>
      We love open source
    </h2>
    <p class="typography.lead offset.after-16">
      Besides contributing to Ember.js via our core team engagements, we maintain a number of projects in the ecosystem that are widely adopted throughout the Ember community.
    </p>
    <div class="media offset.after-12">
      <img class="media.item" src="/assets/images/icons/ember-simple-auth.svg" alt="" />
      <div class="media.body">
        <h3>
          Ember Simple Auth
        </h3>
